---
title: Sheet Pan Walnut-Crusted Chicken with Cheesy Ciabatta & Roasted Broccoli
description: Weeknights feeling busier and more jam-packed than ever? We hear you! That’s why we’re bringing you a quick and easy meal that’s sure to satisfy your whole pack. This week, we’re featuring chicken topped with a crunchy walnut and panko crust, roasted broccoli, toasted cheesy ciabatta, and a savory-sweet honey Dijon dressing for dipping. It’s all ready in just 30 minutes—now that’s a weeknight win.
